schools.name: Martin Luther King Jr. Middle School

data.description: What an amazing property. This property will not last. Property is very clean and manicured. This 2 story beautiful property is very spacious for your entertainment needs and family gatherings. It has a large private patio with a spacious grassy area. It has it's own washer and dryer area convenient for the tenant. Property has an attached spacious 1 car garage. Property offers a clubhouse with pool area, bbq and picnic area.This beautiful property is very close to schools, shopping centers and minutes away from the beach. Don't wait. This property will not last. Call the listing agent.
